<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h1 class="title"><span class="title">以百分比显示电池电量状态</span></h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents pagewide">
<p class="p">顶栏中的<span class="link"><a href="status-icons.html.zh-CN#batteryicons" title="电池图标">状态图标</a></span>显示内置主电池的充电情况，以及其目前是否正在充电。它还可以将电量显示为<span class="link"><a href="power-percentage.html.zh-CN" title="以百分比显示电池电量状态">百分比</a></span>。</p>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-steps"><h2><span class="title">在顶栏显示电池百分比</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">打开<span class="gui"><a href="shell-introduction.html.zh-CN#activities" title="活动概览">活动</a></span>概览后输入<span class="gui">电源</span>。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">点击<span class="gui">电源</span>打开面板。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">切换 <span class="gui">显示电量百分比</span> 开关为开启状态。</p></li>
</ol></div>
</div></div>
</div>
